     function solution(arr) {
           
          let answer = [];
          let sum = 0;
          let min = Number.MAX_SAFE_INTEGER;
          for(let i of arr)
          {
              if(arr[i]%2 === 1)
              {
                sum += arr[i]
                if (arr[i]< min) min = arr[i];
            }
               
            }
            answer.push(sum);
            answer.push(min);
            
            return answer;

        }

        let arr =[12, 77, 38, 41,53, 92, 85]
        console.log(solution(arr));
